text: "\n <div id=\"recipeLeftColumn\">\n  # Robot Color Chooser\n  <hr/>\n  <img\
  \ src=\"./robotColorChooser.png\"/>\n  <div id=\"recipeGoal\">\n   ## Goal:\n  \
  \ Use if and else if statements to set a Robot's pen to a chosen color before drawing\
  \ a shape.\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div id=\"recipeRightColumn\">\n  <div id=\"recipeSteps\"\
  >\n   ## Steps:\n   <ol id=\"stepList\">\n    <li>\n     Ask the user to choose\
  \ a color.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Set the Robot's pen to the chosen color.\n\
  \    </li>\n    <li>\n     Have the Robot draw a shape.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n \
  \    Repeat the above in a loop to test all the supported colors.\n    </li>\n \
  \   <li>\n     Don't forget to use an else statement in case the user enters an\
  \ unrecognized color.\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n  </div>\n </div>\n\n"
